<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Kers 1904</emphasis>
(LISC); Ndoungue near Nkongsamba, 800 m alt., 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Ledermann 6328a</emphasis>
(BM, U); Natchigal, Sanaga waterfall, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">A. &amp; J. Raynal 10542</emphasis>
(P).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Habitat</emphasis>
. River rapids and waterfalls in tropical rain forest.
</paragraph>
